data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Fresno, CA! This beautiful two-story residence boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a host of impressive features that will make you fall in love at first sight.    As you approach the home, you'll be greeted by a charming exterior with stone accents and a well-maintained front yard. The two-car garage and concrete driveway provide ample parking space.    Step inside, and you'll immediately notice the warm and inviting atmosphere created by the wood laminate flooring that runs throughout the entire home. The bedrooms, thoughtfully designed for comfort, offer pristine and clean carpeting, ceiling fans, and sliding closet door.    The dining room is a standout feature, featuring a striking brick accent wall that adds character.    The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a chef's delight. It boasts Formica countertops, abundant dark brown cabinets that exude elegance, and plenty of drawers for all your storage needs. You'll find a gas stove range, oven, microwave, dishwasher, and a spacious two-door fridge, making meal preparation a breeze.    The living room is generously sized and well-lit, with a ceiling fan and embedded ceiling lights to create the perfect ambiance for relaxation and entertainment.    Upstairs, the master bedroom is a spacious retreat with an attached bathroom, a walk-in closet, and a large window that fills the room with natural light. The master bathroom features Formica counters, a walk-in shower, and an adjacent soaking tub for your relaxation and rejuvenation.    The remaining bedrooms are equally charming, with sliding doors on their closets and ample natural light pouring in through the windows. All bathrooms in the home feature Formica countertops and are tastefully designed.    But the true gem of this property is the backyard. It's a spacious haven with fresh new grass and concrete, enclosed by a sturdy wood fence for privacy and security. The perfect spot for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying the California sunshine.  Additionally, this home comes with valuable amenities such as new grass and sprinklers, a water softener, and PAID SOLAR PANELS, which not only enhance your quality of living but also contribute to sustainability. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning Fresno residence your own. It's a place where comfort, style, and functionality come together to create the perfect family home. Schedule a visit today
